  "diagram_type": "stateDiagram",
  "code": "%%{IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker}}}%%\nstateDiagram-v2\n    [IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker] --> Created: Create Todo\n    Created --> InProgress: Start Work\n    Created --> Cancelled: Cancel\n    InProgress --> OnHold: Pause\n    InProgress --> Completed: Complete\n    InProgress --> Cancelled: Cancel\n    OnHold --> InProgress: Resume\n    OnHold --> Cancelled: Cancel\n    Completed --> [IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker]\n    Cancelled --> [IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode]\n\n    state Created {IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker] --> Draft\n        Draft --> ReadyToStart: Finalize\n        ReadyToStart --> [IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController]\n    }\n\n    state InProgress {IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode] --> Started\n        Started --> InReview: Submit for Review\n        InReview --> Started: Request Changes\n        InReview --> [IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode]: Approve\n    }\n\n    state OnHold {IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic] --> Blocked\n        [IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode] --> Deferred\n        Blocked --> [IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream]: Unblock\n        Deferred --> [IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker]: Prioritize\n    }\n\n    state Completed {IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic] --> Done\n        [IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode] --> PartiallyDone\n        Done --> [IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode]\n        PartiallyDone --> [IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream]\n    }",
